# Data fixtures are read byte-for-byte by tests and evals; keep them LF on every
# platform so a Windows checkout (core.autocrlf=true) can't rewrite line endings.
# This repo is line-ending sensitive (ADR-0018: a CRLF prompt copy once flipped a
# Poro judgment); the .jsonl fixtures feed the injection red-team + eval loaders.
*.jsonl text eol=lf
